https://www.codeproject.com/Articles/1264257/Socket-Programming-in-Cplusplus-using-boost-asio-T


install boost library
        Download boost from here: https://www.boost.org/users/download/
        and place it to boost folder.
	Run "./bootstrap.sh". 
 
install C++ compiler if needed
	sudo apt-get install g++

compile and run app for sync server
	./install.sh
	
If error is returned when server starts "bind: Address already in use",
kill any process which uses port 1234 "lsof -ti:1234 | xargs kill -9".	
                                                                  
                                                        

